This study is set out to investigate if paper books better than e-books. In order to research this study there is one question: what causes paper books better than e-books?
The main findings of this study suggest that there are number of reasons for why paper books better than e-book. This study said that reading on a paper book is easier than reading on an e-bbok you can highlighting and book marking the main ideas. Also you can share a paper book with any person. I think reading on a paper book it is more enjoyable for reading and it makes you to keep up with the plot.
Studies have shown that printed books are better for our health. If you want to read on e-book this makes you sit too much time in front of a screen and this will damage your eyes and your whole body.
Finally, as a conclusion, according to the studies reading on a paper book is better than e-book.